{"tid":546046,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講曬 今晚有無超級月亮","createTime":"2018-01-31T06:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T03:42:18.000Z","uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"95238811b7cc4c63105509824867e558c0c81958","tid":546046,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T06:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/105314_220d01f0b77e9b3619434124c483611d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F105314_220d01f0b77e9b3619434124c483611d.png&h=b0c570ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天文奇景預告】1‧31晚觀超級藍月血月！藍月&ne;藍色月亮<br />\n2018/1/27<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/105550_04fc9745d993d7e06a0e9ef863db003e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F105550_04fc9745d993d7e06a0e9ef863db003e.png&h=435e5e91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖為2014年在東京出現的月食。（明報製圖／法新社資料圖片）<br />\n8 photos<br />\n<br />\n天文台溫馨提示，本月31日（星期三）將出現月全食及藍月，若天氣許可，市民在本港大部分面向東方、無障礙物的地方都可以觀賞到，而一般情況下，月全食會出現血月，故美國太空總署（NASA）統稱這個難得一遇的天文現象為「超級藍月血月」（Super Blue Blood Moon）！<br />\n<br />\n根據香港太空館資料，2018年1月31日，月球會於下午5時59分東升，下午6時49分出現半影月食，月全食則於下午8時51分出現，並持續約77分鐘。在全食階段，呈紅色的月球在離東面地平線約36度處的高度，慢慢上升至約53度。整個月食過程於2月1日上午約0時09分結束。<br />\n<br />\n有意觀賞的話，可考慮到東面及天頂不受遮掩的地點觀測。<br />\n<br />\n什麼是超級月亮？<br />\n<br />\n當月球滿月期最接近地球軌道時，會出現「超級月亮」。(月球繞行地球一圈需時約27.3日。) 超級月亮比一般滿月更明亮約30%，望上去的體積較一般滿月大約14%-15%。<br />\n<br />\n什麼是藍月？<br />\n<br />\n於同一個月份出現兩個滿月時，第二個滿月就叫藍月，名稱與顏色並無關係，這個現象約2.5年至2.7年出現一次。<br />\n<br />\n什麼是月全食？<br />\n<br />\n地球的影子可分為兩部分，即本影和半影。當月球完全進入地球的本影，所有直射的陽光均被地球遮擋，月全食便會發生。<br />\n<br />\n什麼是血月？<br />\n<br />\n月全食時，地球厚厚的大氣層把陽光的藍色部分散射，剩下的紅光被折射到月球表面，因此月球呈現紅色。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：美國太空總署（NASA）、香港太空館、<a href=\"http://space.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspace.com&d=avymZ6sZwhxXJiMoodLcDU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=7d87b9ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://space.com</a><br />\n<br />\n整理：丘萃瑩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/hotpick3.php?nodeid=1516805215211&amp;issue=20180127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fhotpick3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1516805215211%26issue%3D20180127&d=avymZ6sZwhxXJiMoodLcDU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=c09d3843\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fhotpick3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1516805215211%26issue%3D20180127&h=4dbd3aaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/hotpick3.php?nodeid=1516805215211&amp;issue=20180127</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b7cf96f4bd5effb3ad59c10e3a2590f430f31624","tid":546046,"uid":1748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:14:37.000Z","msg":"冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多雲"},{"pid":"0e2493755c5131d25927158a01f567c43b825b5d","tid":546046,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7cf96f4bd5effb3ad59c10e3a2590f430f31624","tid":546046,"uid":1748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T08:14:37.000Z","msg":"冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多雲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T09:21:26.000Z","msg":"真係多到癡筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a9976f859ad547aab7c0a99f2eaca88a91d155","tid":546046,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T14:47:32.000Z","msg":"個仆街天清撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" cla